OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FAvailable prison cells for adult males
OL,7,Fin the UK "fell into double figures",
OL,8,Fthe Justice Secretary has claimed.
OL,10,FShabana Mahmood told the annual
OL,11,Fjudges' dinner at Mansion House that,
OL,12,Fwhen she was appointed as Lord
OL,13,FChancellor in the summer, prisons were
OL,14,F"weeks away from running out of space
OL,15,Faltogether" and, as a result, she
OL,16,Fdecided to release some prisoners
OL,17,Fearly.
