OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FAbout 1,100 inmates were due to be
OL,7,Ffreed in a second wave of early
OL,8,Freleases that began on Tuesday under
OL,9,Fthe Government's policy to free up
OL,10,Fprison space.
OL,12,FShe told attendees: "Prisons were not
OL,13,Fjust in crisis, they were on the point
OL,14,Fof collapse. Weeks away from running
OL,15,Fout of space altogether."
