OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FReferring to the disorder across
OL,7,FBritain in the wake of July's
OL,8,FSouthport stabbings, Ms Mahmood said
OL,9,Fthat the "necessity of that decision"
OL,10,Fon early release "was soon apparent",
OL,11,Fbefore adding: "At one point, the
OL,12,Fprison places remaining in the adult
OL,13,Fmale estate fell into double figures."
OL,15,FOn Tuesday, Number 10 said that the
OL,16,FPrime Minister "shares the public's
OL,17,Fanger" at images of prisoners being
OL,18,Freleased early.
