OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer's official spokesman
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Prime Minister shares the
OL,8,Fpublic's anger at these scenes and
OL,9,Fthinks it is shocking that any
OL,10,Fgovernment should ever inherit the
OL,11,Fcrisis that this government has when
OL,12,Fit comes to our prisons.
OL,14,F"But just to be clear, there was no
OL,15,Fchoice not to act. If we had not
OL,16,Facted, we would have faced a complete
OL,17,Fparalysis of the system."
OL,19,FHe said this marks the "second and
OL,20,Ffinal" release of prisoners under the
OL,21,FGovernment's scheme.
