OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FThe 29-year-old told reporters he had
OL,7,Fbeen in prison for seven years for
OL,8,Fkidnap and grievous bodily harm of
OL,9,Fsomeone who owed money to his friend
OL,10,Fand was leaving jail seven weeks
OL,11,Fearlier than planned.
OL,13,FHe said the first thing he would do is
OL,14,F"go to McDonald's, go to my hostel and
OL,15,Ffollow all the rules".
