OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Government plans to
OL,7,Fincrease the maximum period eligible
OL,8,Foffenders can spend under house arrest
OL,9,Ffrom six months to 12 months, Ms
OL,10,FMahmood told MPs in the House of
OL,11,FCommons yesterday.
OL,13,FShe also said she would also address
OL,14,Fthe soaring number of recalls ` the
OL,15,Freturn to prison of those released on
OL,16,Flicence or parole who break probation
OL,17,Frules.
