OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FShe said: "Later this month, I intend
OL,7,Fto review the risk-assessed recall
OL,8,Freview process so that lower risk
OL,9,Fcases can be considered for re-release
OL,10,Fafter they have been recalled to
OL,11,Fprison for two to three months, where
OL,12,Ftheir further detention is no longer
OL,13,Fnecessary to protect the public."
OL,15,FThe Government will also "accelerate"
OL,16,Fthe deportation of foreign nationals,
OL,17,Fas opposed to imprisoning them in the
OL,18,FUK, she said.
