OL,3,CAdult male prison spaces 'fell into
OL,4,Cdouble figures', says Shabana Mahmood
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary has also
OL,7,Flaunched a review into sentencing that
OL,8,Fwill look at handing out more
OL,9,Fpunishments to offenders outside
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FTags are already being used to
OL,13,Fsupervise and monitor offenders
OL,14,Fserving sentences outside prison but
OL,15,Fthe review will consider bringing in
OL,16,Femerging technologies used in other
OL,17,Fcountries, Ms Mahmood said.
