OL,6,FThe prison population is increasing by
OL,7,F4,500 every year and the Government
OL,8,Fhas committed to creating 14,000
OL,9,Fadditional prison spaces.
OL,11,FDavid Gauke, the former justice
OL,12,Fsecretary who has argued that there is
OL,13,Fa strong case for abolishing most jail
OL,14,Fterms of six months or under, will
OL,15,Fchair the review panel.
