OL,6,FHe wrote that the "capacity crisis in
OL,7,Four prisons has meant that, at the
OL,8,Fvery least, we have no choice but to
OL,9,Fpause the increase in the prison
OL,10,Fpopulation", in an article in the New
OL,11,FStatesman on Tuesday.
